實都有職員拎去用, 不過無話一有火職員就要拎滅火筒救火wow."},{"pid":"3fb4fbb02c24c93da1fc2fe7746de2ee4a7ec48e","tid":115974,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁個滅火筒有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n消防例需要<br />\n只係跟例做野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實都有職員拎去用, 不過無話一有火職員就要拎滅火筒救火wow.</blockquote><br />\n只能夠講<br />\n肯去救火係勇敢<br />\n但唔救係冇錯 因為佢地職責真係唔係救火"},{"pid":"65a641c9bfd24d997654b40f5438472ff0f52d92","tid":115974,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"f4250af910e764cc4a664bd41c776a7c9ad9939e","tid":115974,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"ching所言甚是"},{"pid":"683e54debd28034436d063b54ab3ca8a3d250d38","tid":115974,"uid":8951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"個班npc黎架咋<br />\n識閪咩"},{"pid":"67c4086428811d75f16bcd7eb59561af99bc7f6a","tid":115974,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個班npc黎架咋<br />\n識閪咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfacbb685acba15b05505ab7a23de799f70a1e4f","tid":115974,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"估唔到手平時假膠開<br />\n認真起上黎都幾talk得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw<br />\n我都認同樓豬"},{"pid":"7688cc2bff5c0a3490ed52cd61e5d36e74c38523","tid":115974,"uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"我係職員都唔會去救火啦<br />\n<br />\n收得咁少錢, 9完又唔會有錢收"},{"pid":"5b7dc9b890c90da546e2465a7c457d655b85237f","tid":115974,"uid":37733,"like":0,"di